{"tid":238635,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【姦劫犯吊頸亡】民建聯葛珮帆：現評論警方是否失職不公道","createTime":"2017-05-11T06:43:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-11T07:17:53.000Z","uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"058c780ac40bfd28057445a272b17feb48e326c8","tid":238635,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T06:43:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170511/large/1494484278_2758.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170511%2Flarge%2F1494484278_2758.jpg&h=e5774d2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n涉嫌在九龍灣天橋底姦劫22歲少女的48歲林姓男疑犯，昨被警方拘捕，惟今早被發現在秀茂坪警署羈押期間自殺身亡。民建聯立法會議員葛珮帆指，今次事件非常嚴重，警方必須徹查真相，但由於她不了解事件詳情，認為現時評論警方是否有失職是不公道。<br />\n<br />\n葛珮帆又指，警方已有一定程序，確保疑犯不會帶可造成傷害物品進入羈留室，認為警方要委派另一隊警察，徹底調查今次事件，並要完善羈留室情況，令同類事件不再發生。"},{"pid":"529a96fa0013c2b82ef315994663429118fa58da","tid":238635,"uid":24133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T06:44:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59e410fad7c47108479ad2a1ccb56ca0344b8e7d","tid":238635,"uid":87730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T06:47:26.000Z","msg":"葛姐無人搞所以就話嚴重"},{"pid":"16af5810053f7c274d37f5e3f83ca654d8c07988","tid":238635,"uid":107472,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T06:48:20.000Z","msg":"既然都已有一定程序去防止人自殺  都仲比個犯自殺到  咁仲唔係失職<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03055b94437ed14f748cb47beb93de29207c6356","tid":238635,"uid":59518,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T06:49:05.000Z","msg":"認為警方要委派另一隊警察<br />\n<br />\n中国警察<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7aa8100c62725a787e8bc646a90d8c0ee2fed93a","tid":238635,"uid":26451,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T06:49:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cb793d8